Download AirPrint.zip (available on Mediafire), and unzip it into the folder you created. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/6f/Activate-Airprint-Step-2Bullet3.jpg/v4-460px-Activate-Airprint-Step-2Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/6/6f/Activate-Airprint-Step-2Bullet3.jpg/aid1386570-v4-728px-Activate-Airprint-Step-2Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
